{"tid":682573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個人、社會文化、政府的大白象工程","createTime":"2018-05-29T03:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T03:39:57.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"708a69788bec07119adac16d5117a0ab75f69b75","tid":682573,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"政府大白象，有高鐵、港珠澳大橋、蓮塘口岸、三跑道工程<br />\n<br />\n個人文化大白象，包括有：幾十萬的婚宴婚禮、十幾萬的婚禮金器，幾萬蚊婚紗攝影等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1962068/結婚開支升至-33萬%20擺酒佔一半?mtc=10027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1962068%2F%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3-33%E8%90%AC%2520%E6%93%BA%E9%85%92%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%3Fmtc%3D10027&d=Ymjqb4qXfs%2FskuslA%2FANxLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=546ba748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1962068/結婚開支升至-33萬%20擺酒佔一半?mtc=10027</a><br />\n<br />\n如果從文化教育，政府和社會一齊努力，從個人到社會，一齊消滅所有大白象工程，簡化生活，大家生活係咪會更開心，更愉快。減少環境污染之餘，壓力又少又健康。"}]}